</html>
<head>
<title> Event to change bgcolor </title>
<style> 
button { padding: 10px 20px; 
font-size: 20px; 
font-weight: bold; 
border: none; 
border-radius: 7px; 
cursor: pointer; } 
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
